    "course_title": "TRANSPLANTATION, IMMUNOLOGY AND NEPHROLOGY ELECTIVE",
    "description": "Evaluate and treat patients on inpatient and outpatient transplant nephrology services. Common conditions include evaluation of transplant patients with AKI and immunology related problems. Learn the basic principles of immunosuppressant management and rejection management. Review biopsies daily with a pathologist and attend surgical transplant Grand Rounds.",
